The '''Anchorhead Municipal Council''' was the city government of [[Anchorhead/Legends|Anchorhead]] on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. At the insistence of [[Huff Darklighter]], they passed an alien landowner tax sometime after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], in order to persuade [[Throgg]] to sell the [[Lars homestead/Legends|Lars homestead]] to Huff.

